{
  "stem": "766.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was an experience, a good one, a very good one, that such a professor stops me, and I was-- who was I, with-- you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A little student from Poland, he didn't know even, who I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I want to mention before, if it-- if you want in chronological reading, two months before the war, I got married to a man whom I dated and we courted for some times.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't think even, of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever happens, so what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- I don't know, tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got married in June, '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is one day where Jews are allowed to get married.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, now even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, so this was-- Lag BaOmer, is it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got married this day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my new husband-- my husband, this is, was mobilized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he left to the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now, by the way, he never came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, when the war broke out, and this is-- he was supposed to report the first of October, September, when it is?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "September.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already out of work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was already the clinic was finished, out, no more, how it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this-- that time I felt that-- what-- I went back to my mother and my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was still home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know it was such a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no question, what will I do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember, I had some medication to give in case of dehydration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so a father who knew me came with a child, had diarrhea, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
